	OmniPlay is presented with no guarantee of functionality or
	safe operation.  In using this program, you agree that I am
	absolved of any and all liability.  This said, I have made
	efforts to protect OmniPlay's integrity by testing under
	Enforcer and Mungwall, and I'm pretty sure nothing rotten is
	going to happen.  If something rotten does happen, please let
